title: Jenkins and Jonez - LeBron This, LeBron That, and Enes Kanter’s Name Change
itunes:title: Jenkins and Jonez - LeBron This, LeBron That, and Enes Kanter’s Name Change
description:
The guys have an overdue discussion about the LeBron James-Isaiah Stewart situation (3:00) before talking about the fans that LeBron got kicked out (8:30), Enes Kanter changing his name to Enes Kanter Freedom (20:30), Will Smith Will Smith-ing (36:00), and Pete Davidson + Kim Kardashian (57:00).
